{"tid":664554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數人獅子山擬掛「港獨」直幡,  最終不成功","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:25:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4ae02ebea103c861cb47ebdd19166501941d93","tid":664554,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-banner-05132018085250.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-banner-05132018085250.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0e8edec2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-banner-05132018085250.html?encoding=traditional</a><br />\n<br />\n主頁 | 新聞 | 港澳台新聞<br />\n<br />\n數人獅子山擬掛「港獨」直幡 風大未能張開棄下<br />\n2018-05-13<br />\n<br />\n香港獅子山近獅頭位置，周日（13日）被發現有人企圖掛上有關「港獨」的直幡，最終不成功，而涉事人士全部離去。<br />\n<br />\n在周日早上9時許，行山人士發現有五名男女，企圖將一幅大約25米乘7米、寫有「港獨」字句的巨型直幡掛於獅子山，消防員和警員接報後登山，結果在山頂獅頭位置的空地發現直幡，但企圖懸掛的人已不見蹤影；懷疑可能大風關係直幡未能成功張開，掛幡的人士留下離去。<br />\n<br />\n由於直幡面積大，在場的警方與消防人員商討後，將直幡割開五幅紮起帶走，交予相關部門跟進。"},{"pid":"d41fcedca57ae60820662b5c007275cf6c08c790","tid":664554,"uid":116054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/162552_650a33fb36a6237b3fcb4e7ed005b155.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F162552_650a33fb36a6237b3fcb4e7ed005b155.jpeg&h=e508c4a8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}